See that actor?
That's my brother.

17:36.208 --> 17:38.041
-How was that?
-That was great.

17:38.125 --> 17:40.834
That was amazing!
Now, do you think you can say your lines

17:40.917 --> 17:42.917
as well as you sang them in that song?

17:43.000 --> 17:45.709
-Definitely.
-All right, let's go again.

17:52.542 --> 17:53.792
-Ow.
-Sorry.

17:54.125 --> 17:56.208
-Ow.
-Honey, you're just so tense.

17:56.291 --> 17:57.917
I mean... Oh, look,
you have a whole row

17:58.000 --> 17:59.792
-of knots back here.
-That's my spine!

17:59.875 --> 18:03.083
No, it's not! Here, let me just get
this one right here for you.

18:03.208 --> 18:04.333
-[cracks]
-Ooh, OK.

18:04.417 --> 18:06.291
Ow, ow, I can't.
I just can't.

18:06.375 --> 18:08.291
It hurts.
I can't feel my legs.

18:08.375 --> 18:10.792
-It's over.
-I knew it.

18:10.875 --> 18:14.417
Failed again.
I shouldn't even try.

18:14.500 --> 18:16.375
-Aunt Lisa.
-No, it's true, OK?

18:16.458 --> 18:19.709
Everything your mom said about me,
it's true.

18:21.000 --> 18:22.750
You know what Mom says about you?

18:22.834 --> 18:25.417
She says that...
that you're a sweet soul.

18:26.291 --> 18:29.041
And that you're
the best sister in the world.

18:29.500 --> 18:30.333
[soft chuckle]

18:30.417 --> 18:32.959
She trusted you to look out for me
while I'm in LA.

18:34.083 --> 18:37.333
-And I'm so glad that you're here.
-Aww.

18:37.417 --> 18:39.166
-Really?
-Yeah.

18:39.250 --> 18:42.125
You're a great aunt.

18:42.208 --> 18:43.792
-And you know what?
-Hmm?

18:43.875 --> 18:46.500
I think you could totally be
a great massage therapist.

18:46.583 --> 18:49.542
-Oh... I really think I could.
-There you go.

18:49.625 --> 18:52.458
-You know, just research it a little bit.
-Yeah.

18:52.542 --> 18:54.875
Maybe go online, and, uh,

18:54.959 --> 18:58.750
just learn about what feels good,
you know, for humans.

18:58.834 --> 19:02.834
Or I could become
a cat masseuse right now.

19:02.917 --> 19:04.834
Dealer's choice.

19:04.917 --> 19:09.041
You know, whatever you do,
I believe in you.

19:09.125 --> 19:12.625
Ohh, thanks, Stella-bell.

19:12.709 --> 19:13.542
-[cracking]
-[Stella groans]

19:13.625 --> 19:14.625
Oh, sorry.

19:14.709 --> 19:16.750
You know, I'm just...
I'm just gonna go.

19:20.834 --> 19:22.291
[Nick]
Ready for another lesson?

19:24.125 --> 19:25.375
No thanks.

19:26.250 --> 19:28.291
How about some "Three Blind Mice"?

19:28.375 --> 19:30.458
I hear it's a big hit
with the kids these days.

19:30.542 --> 19:31.917
I'm good.

19:32.125 --> 19:33.458
[sighs]

19:35.625 --> 19:36.709
Is something wrong?

19:38.083 --> 19:42.417
Nick, when I was telling DZ
all those things girls like in a guy,

19:42.500 --> 19:45.542
I was really talking about
all the things I like in a guy.

19:46.250 --> 19:47.542
You were?

19:48.125 --> 19:53.041
And if I, let's say, found this guy
who had all of those qualities,

19:53.125 --> 19:56.375
-I'd really hope that he'd like me, too.
-I'd hope so, too.

19:57.500 --> 20:00.125
-Ow.
-Nick, it was you.

20:00.208 --> 20:01.959
OK? I was describing you.

20:03.542 --> 20:05.625
-Forget it.
-Macy, wait.

20:05.709 --> 20:07.041
What?

20:07.875 --> 20:10.458
What I'm trying to say is I like you.

20:10.542 --> 20:13.917
And I've been wanting to tell you
ever since I saw you this summer.

20:14.750 --> 20:17.750
Well, there it is.
What took you so long?

20:17.834 --> 20:19.250
I guess I was just scared.

20:19.333 --> 20:22.750
Mm, if anyone should be scared, it's me.

20:22.875 --> 20:26.000
-Why?
-Because this is crazy.

20:26.083 --> 20:28.959
You're a rock star and I'm your--

20:29.041 --> 20:31.500
-Macy.
-I'm your Macy.

20:32.917 --> 20:36.667
-I like the sound of that.
-Me, too.

20:37.166 --> 20:39.125
This has been such a weird day.

20:39.542 --> 20:41.458
[sighs]
It feels good to be home.

20:41.542 --> 20:44.291
Do you guys think there's
such thing as a cat masseuse?

20:44.375 --> 20:46.125
I mean, this is LA,
so there probably is.

20:46.208 --> 20:48.417
There are like pet therapists
and pet psychics.

20:48.500 --> 20:50.083
That's crazy stuff.
So, what are we doing?

20:50.166 --> 20:52.166
Do you want to order in?
Like, I'm kind of hungry,

20:52.250 --> 20:54.000
but I'm kind of not hungry.
You know?

21:00.333 --> 21:03.166
Hey, Kev. Do you mind going over
tomorrow's lines with me?

21:03.208 --> 21:05.458
Actually, man, you rocked it today.

21:05.583 --> 21:07.917
I think when it comes to movies,
you're a solo act.

21:08.041 --> 21:10.792
-Plus, you're banned from the set.
-Yeah, that too.

21:10.875 --> 21:12.333
[DZ]
Holla!

21:12.792 --> 21:15.000
Oh, best date ever!

21:15.083 --> 21:18.000
-Only date ever.
-So, it went well?

21:18.125 --> 21:19.834
Oh, yeah, Andrea was
definitely feeling me.

21:19.917 --> 21:23.500
Aww, so you remembered all the stuff
I told you about how to act with a girl?

21:23.583 --> 21:24.834
Yeah.

21:24.917 --> 21:27.417
Kinda. I sort of blocked you out.

21:27.500 --> 21:28.417
[door shuts]

21:28.500 --> 21:29.583
Well, I can't wait to meet her.

21:29.709 --> 21:31.750
Yo, DZ, where you at?

21:31.834 --> 21:33.834
Peeps, Andrea; Andrea, peeps.

21:33.917 --> 21:36.208
What up, playas?

21:36.291 --> 21:37.917
Yo, we gotta scoot.
I promised your moms

21:38.000 --> 21:40.417
I'd have you back
to Casa DZ before curfew.

21:40.500 --> 21:42.333
OK.
We can just jump in the cool bus.

21:43.625 --> 21:46.041
[both]
Beep-beep-beep.

21:46.125 --> 21:49.166
[beatboxing]

21:50.542 --> 21:52.125
Come on...

21:54.208 --> 21:55.542
What was that?

21:56.792 --> 21:58.083
<i>[Nick] Next on</i> Jonas LA...

21:58.166 --> 21:59.792
I want you to tell me
everything there is to know

21:59.875 --> 22:03.000
-about being a director.
-You survive the day as my assistant,

22:03.083 --> 22:05.250
and I will tell you
everything you need to know.

22:05.333 --> 22:07.375
-Sweet.
-Mona wants me to kiss Vanessa

22:07.458 --> 22:08.375
today during the shoot.

22:08.458 --> 22:10.291
-How do you feel about that?
-Good.

22:10.375 --> 22:12.542
-Do you have feelings for Joe?
-Yes.

22:13.500 --> 22:15.041
Absolutely, yes.

22:15.125 --> 22:18.208
So if he were to, say,
kiss you during the photo shoot?

22:18.291 --> 22:20.583
Ahh, Joe is gonna kiss me?!

22:20.667 --> 22:22.458
[squeals]

22:22.542 --> 22:24.542
Joe, do your thing.
